                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "\n                              <p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                                        <placeName>San Francisco</placeName>\n                                        <date>March 1./54</date>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>\n                                        <addressee>Mr. Isaac Leeser</addressee>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Dear Friend—</p>\n                              <p>Hardly anything of any interest<lb/> has transpired since my\n                                        last<lb/> Letter, which might serve You as a<lb/> Matter of\n                                        News; however I will drop<lb/> a few Lines to you, to inform\n                                        you of<lb/> a Ball to be given by the “Hebrew<lb/>\n                                        Benevolent Society,” on next “<date>Purim</date>”<lb/> which\n                                        promises so far to be a fine<lb/> affair; a large number of\n                                        tickets<lb/> have already been disposed, and the<lb/>\n                                        managers make active preparations<lb/> to get up a Ball\n                                                  <sic>praiseworty</sic> of the<lb/> society; the\n                                        tickets are sold at $10. The Emani El Congregation<lb/> had\n                                        drawn several plans for a<lb/> synagogue, &amp; have chosen\n                                        one, &amp; are now<lb/> about giving out proposals; the plan\n                                        prescribes<lb/> the Gothic style, &amp; when finished will\n                                        be<lb/> one of the finest synagogues in the\n                                                  <placeName>United<lb/> States</placeName>; the\n                                        Building will be about 50 x 80 feet.<lb/> “Mazos” will be\n                                        sold at 22¢ pr. pound<lb/> The baking of it will shortly be\n                                        begun.</p>\n                              "
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3222rs1z/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
