                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "\n                              <p><persName>Mr. &amp; Mrs. Roggenburger</persName> give their\n                                        best<lb/> Respects to you; &amp; Hoping this will find<lb/>\n                                        you in good spirits &amp; Health</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I remain yours Truly</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">Cauffman H. Meyer</persName>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>P.S. You will have recd a Letter from the<lb/> sec. of the Em.\n                                        congregation about a chason &amp;<lb/> the advertisement</p>\n                              <div>\n                                        <p>\n                                                  <ref target=\"Occident_PDFs/Occ_12_3.pdf\">The above\n                                                  text refers to Occident Volume 12 No. 3 pages 119\n                                                  through 120. Click here to view.</ref>\n                                        </p>\n                              </div>\n                    </body>\n          </text>\n</TEI>\n"
                  },
